ScrollList_GetState
#include Style
#Background wimp 1
Module:	<TextGadgets=>textgadgets/m>
#Line
#Wrap off
Veneer:	<scrolllist_get_state>
Syntax:	ScrollList_GetState
#indent

On entry:
#indent 6
{FCode}r0 = flags
r1 = window object Id
r2 = 0x401a + 0 (16410)
r3 = gadget component Id
{f}
#indent
On exit:
#indent 6
{FCode}r0 = <state=>scrolllist_flags>
{f}
#indent
#Wrap
Purpose:	Method returns in R0 the state of various flags controlling a scroll list. This is distinct from the flags word accessible by method <Gadget_GetFlags>.